author: Reuters Editorial
title: Lululemon holds back forecast on virus uncertainty as results beat
description: Lululemon Athletica Inc beat analysts' estimates for quarterly results on Thursday, lifted by strong holiday season demand, but the athletic apparel maker did not provide a full-year forecast as the coronavirus outbreak fuels uncertainty.
content: (Reuters) - Lululemon Athletica Inc (LULU.O) beat analysts’ estimates for quarterly results on Thursday, lifted by strong holiday season demand, but the athletic apparel maker did not provide a full-year forecast as the coronavirus outbreak fuels uncertainty.… [+2432 chars]
